Khulela Themba Sibiya, Bongani Sandiso Ntanzi, Mthobisi Chris Mncube, Mthokoziseni Zifozonke Mapisa and Sifiso Ntuli are facing charges of murder, attempted murder and robbery. JOHANNESBURG - The suspects charged with the murder of Senzo Meyiwa have refused to enter the dock at the Boksburg Magistrate's Court Five suspects are accused of murdering the late Orlando Pirates and Bafana Bafana goalkeeper. Khulela Themba Sibiya, Bongani Sandiso Ntanzi, Mthobisi Chris Mncube, Mthokoziseni Zifozonke Mapisa and Sifiso Ntuli are facing charges of murder, attempted murder and robbery. READ: Expect more arrests in the Meyiwa murder case: Cele The accused were arrested on Monday in Gauteng and KwaZulu Natal. One of the accused says he does not agree with the charges against him.